c: 16
v: 35
t: "Na babandi babangikanyije (Allah) baravuze bati \"Iyo Allah aza kubishaka, yaba twe cyangwa ababyeyi bacu, nta kindi twari gusenga mu cyimbo cye, ndetse nta n’icyo twari kuziririzaataziririje we ubwe\". Uko ni na ko abababanjirije babigenje. Nonese hari ikindi intumwa zishinzwe kitari ugusohoza ubutumwa mu buryo bugaragara"